nl.jortenmilo.command

Interface CommandEvent.CommandEventListener

  • Enclosing class:
    CommandEvent

    public static interface CommandEvent.CommandEventListener
    Use this interface as listener for all of your Command events. When you add an instance of this interface to the CommandManager it will execute one of the methods when that event has happened.
